        "renderShape": {
          "kind": "markdown"
        },
        "markdown": "# Surface Payload Demo\n\nThis graph exposes multiple declared surfaces.\n\nUse it to verify that a consumer can discover and select:\n- `node.web.summary`\n- `node.web.detail`\n- `node.web.icon`\n\nThe important idea is that these are declared surfaces, not ad-hoc local guesses."
      }
    },
