        "markdown": "## Notes\n\n- The declaration is what makes these surfaces official.\n- Consumers should discover surfaces from the target graph.\n- `summary`, `detail`, and `icon` are consumer-facing payload choices.\n- This graph is intentionally small so it can act as a stable target for surface-selection tests."
